{"tid":2246083,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有沒人鐘意左戴口罩?","createTime":"2020-10-16T18:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T00:36:45.000Z","uid":124400,"like":57,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"964a2a9e72f7fc6d721ca9132066ab09c235e874","tid":2246083,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:02:53.000Z","msg":"作為一個毒撚，真係搵唔到理由討厭口罩，原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 出到街無人知你係邊個，更加唔怕撞到同事和朋友！<br />\n2. 10 個毒撚，9 個唔鐘意刷牙，口罩幫你拉近人與人之間嘅距離！<br />\n3. 返工開會唔小心講左無聲粗口？口罩幫你擋下一切誤會！<br />\n4. 個樣唔掂？口罩至少幫你抵消一半問題，而且同女神搭訕嘅機會又高左！<br />\n5. 讓社會更平等更美好，上堂答問題，做 Project 搵 Groupmate，只要死都唔除口罩，至少我地仲有機會！加上毒撚天生的邏輯力，反擊靚仔 Player 簡直 Easy！<br />\n<br />\n除罩？不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8631c951db830bc0ad2d498abcf529eea3c24667","tid":2246083,"uid":124400,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:11:16.000Z","msg":"6. 毒撚通常具有迷人的眼睛，戴口罩將更加突顯我們的魅力，同 push up bra 功能相若"},{"pid":"3e5fcac0efc869dbaa01c0e1c02d969dca5d2c03","tid":2246083,"uid":124400,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:13:02.000Z","msg":"7. 消除尷尬，同女神傾計就算諗唔到話題，表情尷尬都可以扮諗緊野"},{"pid":"2927ca618110e9edadff4780167fccfb0db46b6c","tid":2246083,"uid":370479,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:14:39.000Z","msg":"我鐘意右戴多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c507591f6bce08d05b55a606288d1c1618e584","tid":2246083,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:15:00.000Z","msg":"8. 如果女神除低口罩，我地又唔小心掉轉左嚟戴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bef21044b8262cc3d253c02d633dee00a4c7a19","tid":2246083,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"9. 條底褲唔覺意整濕左？用口罩頂住先囉 (未試過）"},{"pid":"4fce6c17313beb689e10c08f10c8bfa3d15b6a63","tid":2246083,"uid":124400,"like